This paper is primarily focused on cybersecurity and threat intelligence, which falls under the category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also describes the use of machine learning algorithms to learn association rules, which could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The system design and deployment aspects of the paper could be categorized under cs.SE (Software Engineering). Finally, the paper discusses the use of the system to predict and prevent cyber attacks, which could be categorized under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
